# NOC Dashboard Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   get_active_alarms — Retrieve all active alarms from the NMS
#   get_alarm_details — Get detailed information about a specific alarm
#   get_noc_dashboard — Get current NOC dashboard metrics and network health
#   send_notification — Send notifications to NOC team members and stakeholders
#   acknowledge_alarm — Acknowledge an alarm in the NMS
